Invocation Name: tub tales
des:
Play an interactive science fiction-themed story with prompts. Get ready for laughs and giggles as players fill in the blanks. 
A little boy you name lives in a bathtub toy world of swimming BEAM robots, BEAM robots have simple emergent A.I and are made from both passive and digital components, but do they live, explore in this story, and join the little boy on reflecting if you are more than A.I? or just an autopilot in a machine somewhere or a toy somewhere?
